{"body":{"coverUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/63","type":"COUNTRY_MP","status":"UNCURRENT","id":32,"name":"葉忠倫","electorate":"苗栗縣第四選區<br>竹南、後龍、造橋","weight":2,"contact":"聯絡我們","support":"支持我們","politics":"政策","declaration":"科技強棒 揮出苗栗新未來","areaId":7,"areaName":"苗栗縣","createdAt":"2022-05-24T09:05:52.312Z","candidateAttachments":[{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/962","id":775,"attachmentType":"url","attachmentUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SRJBdWnafFg","attachmentName":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SRJBdWnafFg&ab_channel=%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8F2022%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E5%85%AC%E8%81%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89","title":"葉忠倫_競選宣言","content":null,"weight":99,"createdAt":"2022-06-16T07:39:50.783Z"},{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/961","id":774,"attachmentType":"image/png","attachmentUrl":"https://2022.npp.vote/public/uploads/5.png","attachmentName":"29dfa11c-0869-4d12-8802-a5744dbe8569_.png","title":" ","content":null,"weight":5,"createdAt":"2022-06-16T07:38:16.325Z"},{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/960","id":773,"attachmentType":"image/png","attachmentUrl":"https://2022.npp.vote/public/uploads/4.png","attachmentName":"daf7a6f5-5358-49bd-836c-e24943fecfa6_.png","title":" ","content":null,"weight":4,"createdAt":"2022-06-16T07:38:15.765Z"},{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/959","id":772,"attachmentType":"image/jpeg","attachmentUrl":"https://2022.npp.vote/public/uploads/3.jpg","attachmentName":"1ef5768f-deaf-424e-9835-cad9434a9a65_.jpg","title":" ","content":null,"weight":3,"createdAt":"2022-06-16T07:38:15.241Z"},{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/958","id":771,"attachmentType":"image/jpeg","attachmentUrl":"https://2022.npp.vote/public/uploads/2.jpg","attachmentName":"5e732b3e-4298-4689-93a1-df19c90f5830_.jpg","title":" ","content":null,"weight":2,"createdAt":"2022-06-16T07:38:14.748Z"},{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/957","id":770,"attachmentType":"image/png","attachmentUrl":"https://2022.npp.vote/public/uploads/1.png","attachmentName":"f3db9971-52cd-4df7-97a1-610f42ca98b0_.png","title":" ","content":null,"weight":1,"createdAt":"2022-06-16T07:38:14.646Z"}],"candidateContacts":[{"id":40,"title":"地址","content":"苗栗縣竹南鎮新南街35號B5-10F","createdAt":"2022-05-30T09:05:52.544Z"},{"id":41,"title":"電話","content":"0910 582 675","createdAt":"2022-05-30T09:05:52.631Z"}],"candidateDeclaration":{"id":29,"title":"很多人說政治很複雜，但我對於政治的解讀是，這是我們可以為家鄉帶來改變的一個方式","content":"<p>苗栗是我生活了 40 年的家鄉，更是我成家育兒的所在，因此我比誰都希望這片土地能夠擁有更好的未來，與時俱進，成為一個更宜居進步的城市。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>然而我們也發現，苗栗整體的改變步伐不僅比其他縣市緩慢，內部更有一定的城鄉差距。有些地方受惠於科技廊帶而有了正向發展，有些地方還依舊停滯不前。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>要帶來更多正向改變，需要更多真正願意付出的人，所以我決定投身加入行列。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>我是化工背景的工程師出身，在科技業工作了 15 年，深深了解產業需求和環境保護之間的拉扯<strong>，</strong>因此希望能以最嚴謹的態度來把關，做到最好的兼顧。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>我是兩個孩子的爸爸，深切感受到雙薪家庭的育兒重擔，再加上長輩的照護，讓我非常關心育兒及長照政策，如何確實減輕三明治世代的負擔。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>尤其在這個薪資漲不過物價和房價的年代，更需要政府拿出實際方案，讓苗栗成為安心宜居的城市。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>希望所有對苗栗發展問題感同身受的朋友，能夠給我一個服務的機會，讓我用我對家鄉的熱忱和工程師的專業，與大家共同打造更好的新苗栗。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>科技強棒，揮出苗栗新未來！</strong></p>","createdAt":"2022-05-30T09:05:52.514Z"},"candidateEducations":[{"id":69,"title":"中興大學化工所 碩士","content":null,"weight":1,"createdAt":"2022-05-30T09:05:52.617Z"}],"candidateExperiences":[{"id":141,"title":"半導體工程師","content":null,"weight":1,"createdAt":"2022-05-30T09:05:52.540Z"}],"candidatePolitics":[{"id":1120,"title":"乾淨政治,透明議會 ","content":" 定期公布助理名單、職稱\n◼定期報告議會工作成果\n◼清白參選，不包工程，不收紅包","weight":6,"createdAt":"2022-09-13T08:01:57.778Z"},{"id":1121,"title":"多元學習，友善親子","content":"◼強化幼教管理與評鑑，提高教保員待遇\n◼推動老舊公園翻新，共融參與設計\n◼爭取公民營親子空間設置\n","weight":5,"createdAt":"2022-09-13T08:04:22.959Z"},{"id":1123,"title":"全民運動，健康樂活","content":"◼活化閒置空間，轉為體育使用\n◼提升運動風氣，推廣全齡運動\n◼監督竹南全民運動館的興建品質","weight":3,"createdAt":"2022-09-13T08:20:20.099Z"},{"id":1122,"title":"道路平權，交通順暢","content":"◼ 盤點高風險路段道路設計\n◼建構友善行人的通行環境\n◼推動騎樓整平化，建立無障礙通行空間","weight":3,"createdAt":"2022-09-13T08:17:14.577Z"},{"id":1124,"title":"醫療照護 ，全面升級","content":"◼ 強化社區關懷據點功能\n◼提升長照機構管理與照顧品質\n◼補助偏鄉醫療交通、強化巡迴醫療","weight":2,"createdAt":"2022-09-13T08:40:02.290Z"},{"id":1125,"title":"環境保護，我來監督","content":"◼ 增加河川水質、空氣汙染稽查人力\n◼強化一般及事業廢棄物稽查與管理\n◼提升汙水下水道接管率\n","weight":1,"createdAt":"2022-09-13T09:18:19.751Z"}],"candidateSocial":{"id":31,"line":null,"facebook":"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100079953846760","email":"webbet1943@gmail.com","instagram":null,"youtube":null,"createdAt":"2022-05-30T09:05:52.557Z"},"candidateSupports":[{"id":63,"title":"政治獻金專戶","content":" ","weight":2,"createdAt":"2022-05-30T09:05:52.550Z"},{"id":64,"title":"看板和志工應援","content":"mailto:webbet1943@gmail.com ","weight":1,"createdAt":"2022-05-30T09:05:52.629Z"}]}}